// Navigate to the projects page by clicking on 'Projects' link in the sidebar
await page.locator('a[href="/dashboard/projects"]').click();

// Click the 'New Project' button at index 20 to open the project creation form.
await page.locator('a.inline-flex.items-center.px-4.py-2.border.border-transparent.rounded-md.shadow-sm.text-sm.font-medium.text-white.bg-primary[href="/dashboard/projects/new"]').nth(20).click();

// Navigate to the 'Proposals' page by clicking the link at index 4 in the sidebar
await page.locator('a:nth-of-type(4)').click();

// Click the 'Orders' navigation link to test navigation to the Orders page
await page.locator('a.px-3.py-2.rounded-md.text-sm.font-medium.transition-colors.text-gray-700[href="/orders"]').click();

// Click the 'refresh the page' button to attempt to reload the page and see if the ngrok error resolves.
await page.locator('button:nth-of-type(2)').click();
